project 
   : default-build 
      release 
   : requirements
      <library>/googlebenchmark <threading>single
      <variant>debug:<define>SOMEMACRO # If compiling debug, define SOMEMACRO
      #<cxxflags>"-fsanitize=float-cast-overflow "
